article:
'DU145' ('DU-145') and PC3 human prostate cancer cell lines are the "classical"
cell lines of prostatic cancer. DU145 cells have moderate metastatic
potential compared to PC3 cells which have high metastatic potential.

The DU145 cell line was derived from brain metastasis. DU145 are not hormone
sensitive and donât express PSA (Prostate Specific Antigen).
